## 4. EXECUTION TARGETS

| Mode | Target |
|------|----------|
| `:auto` | `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep-research-auto.yaml` |
| `:confirm` or interactive choice | `.opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep-research-confirm.yaml` |

