.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/spec.md-75-- A post-scaffold manifest step for `ready`: call the canonical minter supplied by the P3 eligibility implementation, then verify the returned manifest is valid and fresh before reporting compiled-ready.
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/spec.md:76:- The `legacy` state: do not mint a manifest; report the generated hub as legacy by construction.
