.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/spec.md-79-- JSON and Markdown report additions, deterministic fixtures, Vitest coverage, and README/CLI documentation.
