.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/spec.md-241-- What stable machine-readable P0 status-probe interface will return the cause behind a legacy sentinel?
