.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-166-Package invariants:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-167-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md:168:- The root file is always `manual-testing-playbook.md`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-169-- Per-feature files live in root-level category folders.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-170-- Category directories use descriptive kebab-case names such as `category-name` (no numeric prefix).
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-171-- Per-feature files use stable kebab-case slugs such as `feature-name.md`; no numeric file prefix.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md:172:- Per-feature snippet order is defined by the root playbook listing order.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md:173:- Display order is owned by the root playbook index (`manual-testing-playbook.md`), not the folder name.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-174-- Benchmark tier is owned by the per-feature file's optional `stage:` frontmatter field (`routing` default, or `holdout`/`negative`), not by a filename token.
