.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-277-- `SKIP` with a specific sandbox blocker
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md-278-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/SKILL.md:279:Do not classify scenarios as `UNAUTOMATABLE`.
