.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-63-- A skill has 5+ distinct features that need manual validation.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-64-- Automated tests do not cover integration-level or end-to-end behavior.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-65-- Multiple operators (human or AI) will execute the same test suite.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:66:- Release readiness requires structured evidence collection.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-67-- Realistic orchestration behavior matters, including sub-agent or alternate-CLI usage.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-68-
