.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:78:  YES -> Does it need structured evidence for release?
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:79:    YES -> Create root playbook + root-level per-feature files
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-80-    NO  -> Create lightweight checklist in spec folder
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-81-  NO -> Document test steps inline in spec folder tasks.md
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-82-```
