.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-104-- `NNN`: zero-padded 3-digit sequence number starting at 001.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-105-- IDs are unique across the entire playbook.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-106-- Gaps are allowed; do not renumber published IDs.
