.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-249-- `PASS`: all acceptance checks true
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:250:- `PARTIAL`: core behavior works but non-critical evidence or metadata is incomplete
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-251-- `FAIL`: expected behavior missing, contradictory output, or critical check failed
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-252-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-253-### Feature Verdict Rules
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-254-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:255:- `PASS`: all mapped scenarios for feature are `PASS`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:256:- `PARTIAL`: at least one mapped scenario is `PARTIAL`, none are `FAIL`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:257:- `FAIL`: any mapped scenario is `FAIL`
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-258-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-259-Hard rule:
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:260:- Any critical-path scenario `FAIL` forces feature verdict to `FAIL`.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-261-
