.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-404-### Recommended Orchestration Process
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-405-
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-406-1. Restate the user request in plain user language.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md:407:2. Decide whether the scenario should stay local, delegate to sub-agents, or invoke another CLI/runtime.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-408-3. Execute the deterministic steps exactly as written.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-409-4. Compare the observed output against the desired user-visible outcome.
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/create-manual-testing-playbook/assets/manual-testing-playbook-template.md-410-5. Return a concise final answer that a real user would understand.
