309:This category validates the runtime-neutral `mk-post-edit-quality` post-edit quality router shared by the OpenCode plugin adapter and the Claude Code `PostToolUse` hook. Scenarios here exercise the real dispatch/router core, the real Claude hook binary, and the real OpenCode plugin module end-to-end — independent of skill-advisor routing or surface detection. IDs in this category are descriptive kebab-slugs, not numbered `{PREFIX}-NNN` ids.
