52:## 2. SMART ROUTING
54:Routing is **registry-driven**. `mode-registry.json` is the single source of truth; the hub reads it and does not re-derive the mapping. The advisor routes any design query to the single identity `sk-design`; the hub then picks the mode. Canonical `/interface:*` commands and their `/design:*` compatibility aliases resolve to the same stable mode IDs.
